                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Housing:</strong> Provide a spacious, well-ventilated hutch or enclosure with adequate bedding.</li>
                    <li><strong>Temperature:</strong> Keep the environment cool in summer and warm in winter, avoiding extreme temperatures.</li>
                    <li><strong>Enrichment:</strong> Include toys and safe chew items to keep rabbits entertained and active.</li>
                </ul>
                <p>Regularly clean the living area to maintain hygiene and prevent diseases.</p>
            </div>
