                <p>Preventing common health issues is crucial for maintaining a healthy rabbit:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Gastrointestinal Issues:</strong> Ensure a high-fiber diet and avoid sudden changes in feed.</li>
                    <li><strong>Respiratory Infections:</strong> Provide proper ventilation and avoid exposure to damp or drafty conditions.</li>
                    <li><strong>Ear Mites:</strong> Regularly check for signs of mites and consult a vet for treatment if needed.</li>
                </ul>
                <p>Schedule regular veterinary check-ups and maintain good hygiene practices.</p>
